WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.015
Myocarditis is an inflammatory disease of the

00:00:03.015 --> 00:00:03.446
myocardium.

00:00:03.446 --> 00:00:06.462
This presentation reviews the adverse effects of

00:00:06.462 --> 00:00:09.477
myocarditis and their clinical implications for patient

00:00:09.477 --> 00:00:11.200
management and risk stratification.
